How to use the service:
Take the item(s) to be scanned to any library circulation desk. Present your faculty ID and
state that the item is for scanning. If there is more than one item to be scanned, please
prioritize the order in which items should be scanned. If you need the item after it is scanned,
ask the circulation desk staff person to place a hold on the item for you
